#         'License Plates Are Going Digital',
#         '{"blocks":[{"key":"3v84b","text":"\"In 2008, Neville Boston envisioned simplifying vehicle registration. Today, it''s a reality with the RPlate Pro.\"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":113,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":113,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":113,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":113,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"1paag","text":"\nLong before animated sloths took on the DMV counter in \"Zootopia,\" Neville Boston, CEO of Reviver Auto, aimed to streamline the vehicle registration process. He sought a way for drivers to update their registration automatically and electronically, avoiding the notorious DMV wait times.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":288,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":288,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":288,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":1,"length":287,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c0jb7","text":"\"People often wonder how I worked around the DMV,\" Boston explains. \"I didn''t. I worked with the DMV. They became like partners. But the process is the process.\" Despite the collaboration, it took Boston years to transform his idea into reality – a digital license plate called RPlate Pro.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":289,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":289,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":289,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":289,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"8ag3a","text":"The RPlate Pro, available in California, employs e-ink technology (similar to Kindle e-readers) to display license plate numbers and registration dates in black and white. Through the RConnect platform, drivers can easily renew and pay the DMV online, with the digital license plate updating automatically. No more waiting for stickers or enduring DMV visits.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":359,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":359,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":359,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":359,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"bo4g7","text":"Installation is straightforward, connecting to a car''s battery. \"It takes no power to show an image,\" Boston notes, ensuring the plate always functions as a license plate. If removed, it sends a text message to the owner, displaying \"STOLEN\" on the plate via the RConnect platform.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":281,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":281,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":281,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":281,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"1fngg","text":"The RPlate Pro isn''t just a license plate; it''s a smart plate. Owners can display different specialty plates daily to support causes, and it can show emergency messages like Amber Alerts or severe weather warnings. Businesses can even put ads on their tags, with a messaging component for legally parked vehicles.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"c1p0q","text":"Fleet owners benefit from remote registration renewal and real-time location tracking for each vehicle. The plates can facilitate paying bridge tolls, and future updates may enable interaction with parking meters.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":213,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":213,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":213,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":213,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"cgpii","text":"Addressing concerns about physical vulnerability and digital security, Boston emphasizes compliance and privacy. The e-ink screen is designed for readability, similar to safety glass in windshields. Privacy features, including optional GPS embedding, allow drivers to control information sharing.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":296,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":296,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":296,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":296,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"dqjob","text":"Currently available in California and approved for use in Arizona, Texas, and Florida, the RPlate Pro comes at a price – $599 for the license plate and an additional $8 per month for the service plan. Boston anticipates the cost to decrease as the product gains traction. The goal? \"To have one on every vehicle.\"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":313,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}},{"key":"fnc4b","text":"While the RPlate Pro may be an investment, it offers an accessible way to bring connectivity to older vehicles, both privately owned and part of business fleets. ReviverAuto plans to expand the RPlate''s availability in nearly a dozen states in 2018, with international deployment on the horizon. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":295,"style":"color-rgb(55,65,81)"},{"offset":0,"length":295,"style":"fontsize-16"},{"offset":0,"length":295,"style":"fontfamily-Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Noto Sans\", sans-serif, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\", \"Noto Color Emoji"},{"offset":0,"length":296,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"text-align":"start"}}],"entityMap":{}}'
